    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, dependable option for anyone in need of a functional daily driver. While the exterior shows some age with minor scratches and the interior has seen better days, the engine and transmission remain in good working order. It has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure it starts up every morning, though a new owner might want to address some of the cosmetic wear and tear. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility and reliability over a showroom finish.",
