    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a high standard of mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Having undergone a comprehensive professional evaluation, this unit offers a seamless blend of performance and comfort. It remains a premier choice for the discerning driver who demands a well-maintained, reliable motorcar that delivers a refined experience on every journey.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
